26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_bios_bit.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:33 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include <subdev/bios.h>
30#include <subdev/bios/bit.h>
31
32int
33bit_entry(struct nvkm_bios *bios, u8 id, struct bit_entry *bit)
34{
35 if (likely(bios->bit_offset)) {
36 u8 entries = nvbios_rd08(bios, bios->bit_offset + 10);
37 u32 entry = bios->bit_offset + 12;
38 while (entries--) {
39 if (nvbios_rd08(bios, entry + 0) == id) {
40 bit->id = nvbios_rd08(bios, entry + 0);
41 bit->version = nvbios_rd08(bios, entry + 1);
42 bit->length = nvbios_rd16(bios, entry + 2);
43 bit->offset = nvbios_rd16(bios, entry + 4);
44 return 0;
45 }
46
47 entry += nvbios_rd08(bios, bios->bit_offset + 9);
48 }
49
50 return -ENOENT;
51 }
52
53 return -EINVAL;
54}
